Sello Theletsane JOHANNESBURG- ANC spokesperson Pule Mabe has been accused of sexual harassment by his former personal assistant. Mabe has denied the woman’s claims while the ANC has in a statement said the matter is under investigation. Africa News24-7 has decided to publish the woman’s letter addressed to ANC Deputy Secretary-General Jessie Duarte in full. However, we are withholding the woman’s identity. Click here to read the woman’s full letter of grievance